description:
Is this your future IT development infrastructure? All run in Amazon Cloud.

Plus Amazon S3 for static content and storage and Puppet as Configuration Management?
comments.comment: Though I would sub Mercurial for Git, add Gradle for a build tool and other Atlassian tools.; +Dean Budd say something Deano. This is private and business confidential post. Hahaha ...; I'm all for the cloud! :-)
